# Shared exclude list for `bca --paths . --exclude-from .bcaignore ...`.
# Mirrors the deny-set the self-scan workflow and the local baseline
# refresh both walk. Keep this file and `.bca-baseline.toml` in sync —
# the baseline keys are sensitive to which files the walker visits.
#
# Patterns use the same `./`-prefix convention as the walker's emitted
# form so they match `--paths .` output one-to-one.
#
# Blank lines and lines whose first non-whitespace character is `#`
# are skipped (`.gitignore`-style).

./tree-sitter-*/**
./tests/**
./**/tests/**
./enums/**
./target/**
./big-code-analysis-book/**
./docs/**
./packaging/**
./utils/**
./xtask/**
./generate-grammars/**
./man/**
./abuild-keys/**
./**/examples/**
./check-*.py
